contentrichtext.text: '''[[Ordos]]''' is a city and district in Inner Mongolia. '''Ordos''' may also refer to: *[[Ordos Loop]] of the Yellow River, a region of China *[[Ordos Desert]], in Inner Mongolia *[[Ordos Mongols]], a Mongol tribe that has inhabited the Ordos region since the 15th century *[[Ordos culture]], prehistorical culture *[[Ordos Mongolian]], the variety of Mongolian spoken by the Ordos people *[[Ordos International Circuit]], a race track in Ordos City *[[House Ordos]], a fictional organisation in 'Dune' spin-offs *Ordos, fictional groups in [[Inquisition (Warhammer 40,000)]] {{disambiguation}}
